reviewText: It is Amazon corporate policy to allow you to order this women's DVD and they ship you the men's instead.  This is not only illegal but immoral. It is an unethical business practice and indicative of the moral lapses in America.  It is theft short and simple.
Somehow, there must be a mistake, because I ordered the Womens Championship Final 2008 and I got the Mens.  Come on Amazon, please fix this?  The men's championship was great.  clyde
